850
00:59:13,066 --> 00:59:15,944
Kenapa saya asyik menangis?

851
00:59:21,408 --> 00:59:22,450
Dal-mi.

852
00:59:24,577 --> 00:59:26,288
Nenek kata

853
00:59:29,833 --> 00:59:31,876
dia nak tengok awak tersenyum

854
00:59:33,586 --> 00:59:34,921
untuk masa yang lama.

855
00:59:39,134 --> 00:59:42,679
Jadi cuba senyum.

856
00:59:50,353 --> 00:59:51,521
Saya nampak macam menangis?

857
00:59:51,604 --> 00:59:53,898
Ya. Sedikit.

858
00:59:53,982 --> 00:59:56,401
Tak. Nampak sangat ketara.

859
00:59:56,901 --> 00:59:58,153
- Nampak ketara?
- Ya.

860
00:59:59,154 --> 01:00:00,363
Tak bagus kalau begitu.

861
01:00:01,323 --> 01:00:03,074
Saya tak nak nenek tahu saya menangis.

862
01:00:03,783 --> 01:00:06,870
Apa saya patut buat?
Saya tak tahu nak buat apa.

863
01:00:07,579 --> 01:00:09,622
- Saya nampak okey?
- Ya.

864
01:00:09,706 --> 01:00:10,874
Bahagian ini.

865
01:00:11,708 --> 01:00:12,792
- Sebelah sini?
- Ya.

866
01:00:34,814 --> 01:00:37,025
Kamu dah balik? Dah makan?

867
01:00:38,360 --> 01:00:39,319
Dah.

868
01:00:39,402 --> 01:00:40,945
Biar saya potong kuku nenek.

869
